        @Deprecated
public static String parseUnitId(String target)
        Deprecated. 
        UNIT_IDs MUST only contain the following characters: 'A'-'Z', 'a'-'z', '0'-'9', and '_'. UNIT_IDs SHOULD consist of the resource identifier plus the resources internal unit id. A resource is anything that is generating mzTab files.
